data.name: duykhoa_tka
data.message: A leader is one who knows the way, goes the way and shows the way.

data.name: anhpham_n
data.message: Everything has beauty, but not everyone sees it.

data.name: nguyen_khang
data.message: Peace does not mean one where no noise, no trouble, and no toil. When we are in a storm, we still feel the calm of mind. That is the real meaning of peace!
